      "author_association" : "OWNER",
      "body" : "When using hardened derivation, child private keys are effectively generated using a stream cipher using the master private key as seed. This is standard practice when generating keys.\n\nTo anyone who does not know the seed, the resulting output is indistinguishable from random, and thus has the same security properties as random keys.",
